= Building openssl 1.0.1c
=======================================================================
Build Machine:
	Thor
	Linux thor 2.6.38-8-generic #42-Ubuntu SMP Mon Apr 11 03:31:24 UTC 2011 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux
	Linux Mint 11 Katya \n \l

	bm1, bm2
	Linux bm2 3.2.0-23-generic #36-Ubuntu SMP Tue Apr 10 20:39:51 UTC 2012 x86_64 x86_64 x86_64 GNU/Linux
	Linux Mint 13 Maya \n \l

Build Commands:
	. /usr/share/cross-compile/arm-sourcery-glibc/SOURCE_ME

	// XXX: The below command optimizes for speed
	./Configure --prefix=/tmp/$(whoami)/openssl linux-armv4

	// XXX: The below command optimizes for size
	./Configure --prefix=/tmp/$(whoami)/openssl linux-armv4:gcc:-Os

	// ATS FIXME: The OpenSSL Makefile contains a race-condition because "make -j12" fails with linker
	//	errors, however "make" works. This was found on "bm2".
	make -j 4

	make install
